Subject: kernelbase: Support the Image File Execution Options debugger (macOS/Steam)

Upstream-format IFEO Debugger support (implementation + kernel32 conformance test). Lets the Steam webhelper wrapper attach via the image's Image File Execution Options 'Debugger' value, keeping steamwebhelper.exe byte-identical to Valve's. Mirrors Whisky wine patch 0001 / the upstream submission by Yuanyuan Chen <cyyever@outlook.com>.

